songs.title: Double Vision
songs.lyrics:
Snippet

[Chorus: Lauren &  Dinah]
Somebody help me
Somebody help me, yeah
‘Cause I’m in love with these two guys
But I ain’t got the heart to tell 'em
Somebody help me
Somebody help me now
'Cause I just can't keep up with 'em
But I gotta make a decision

[Post-Chorus: Camila]
(I've got) Double vision
(I've got) Double vision
(I've got) Double vision
(I've got) Double vision
